Actions.Text: REFERRED TO TOURISM, PARKS, ARTS AND SPORTS DEVELOPMENT

Title: Extends the expiration date of free one day admission to the zoological park
Summary: Extends the expiration date of free one day admission to the zoological park to December 31, 2030.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend chapter 383 of the laws of 1991, relating to the incorporation of the New York Zoological Society, in relation to extending the expiration date of free one day admission to the zoological park
